divs: Sighting DetailsWe own a ranch and for the past six years there has been things in the sky with pulsating lights that can move straight up and down and diagonal or move miles away within a split second. The neighbors I have talked to have also noticed. When I first noticed them six years ago they were more towards monarch pass, now they are across the field over our other house and also over the hill across our road. We see them mostly in the summer but they have been around alot this winter.
Summary: see at night when not cloudy
